00:45:29,630 --> 00:45:31,710
So the security

868
00:45:31,710 --> 00:45:33,560
becomes tighter.

869
00:45:34,190 --> 00:45:35,670
Is Leader out?

870
00:45:35,670 --> 00:45:36,920
That’s rare.

871
00:45:37,950 --> 00:45:38,670
Alight,

872
00:45:38,670 --> 00:45:40,150
get some rest after the meal.

873
00:45:40,150 --> 00:45:41,120
Don’t stay up too late.

874
00:45:43,230 --> 00:45:44,230
Yan,

875
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:46,710
I mean you.

876
00:45:46,710 --> 00:45:48,190
Starting from tomorrow,

877
00:45:48,190 --> 00:45:50,000
no more lie-ins.

878
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:52,120
You’ve been slack lately.

879
00:45:53,230 --> 00:45:54,190
Mr. Ma,

880
00:45:54,710 --> 00:45:56,710
<i>Liquor</i>
what’s going on outside?

881
00:45:58,280 --> 00:45:59,800
Whatever it is,

882
00:45:59,800 --> 00:46:01,670
it has nothing to do with you, got it?

883
00:46:01,670 --> 00:46:02,710
Are you done?

884
00:46:02,710 --> 00:46:04,190
Go upstairs to sleep.

885
00:46:04,630 --> 00:46:05,600
Go!

886
00:46:08,190 --> 00:46:09,080
Go away.

887
00:46:18,390 --> 00:46:19,890
When will she grow up?

888
00:46:20,600 --> 00:46:22,950
Have a good night.

889
00:46:23,360 --> 00:46:24,040
Fei.

890
00:46:24,360 --> 00:46:24,950
You too.

891
00:46:24,950 --> 00:46:25,560
Sure.

892
00:46:37,160 --> 00:46:40,670
♪Stars flow like river♪

893
00:46:41,730 --> 00:46:45,330
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

894
00:46:45,900 --> 00:46:49,970
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

895
00:46:50,220 --> 00:46:53,860
♪I will never be alone♪

896
00:46:53,860 --> 00:46:57,980
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

897
00:46:58,400 --> 00:47:02,830
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

898
00:47:03,490 --> 00:47:08,050
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

899
00:47:08,280 --> 00:47:12,910
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

900
00:47:13,100 --> 00:47:16,930
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

901
00:47:17,150 --> 00:47:21,840
♪When I go across the world for you♪

902
00:47:22,100 --> 00:47:25,840
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

903
00:47:26,170 --> 00:47:31,260
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

904
00:47:31,260 --> 00:47:35,200
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

905
00:47:35,200 --> 00:47:39,730
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

906
00:47:40,350 --> 00:47:47,450
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

907
00:47:48,190 --> 00:47:52,820
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

